{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "abf52d6d-fb42-45c3-af7f-eab31d0ec96c", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/abf52d6d-fb42-45c3-af7f-eab31d0ec96c@1.pkg/1772597712025/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597713097", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/abf52d6d-fb42-45c3-af7f-eab31d0ec96c@1.pkg/1772597712025/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597713097"}, "identifier": "abf52d6d-fb42-45c3-af7f-eab31d0ec96c", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>本题考查集体生活的作用。</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>A：划龙舟需要指挥员的鼓点指挥，划桨员保持一致的划桨力度和频率，齐喊口号挥桨劈浪，体现了协作共赢的精神，因此A正确</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>B：&ldquo;只有在集体协作中才能实现自身进步&rdquo;说法过于绝对，有时个体的改变思想或是改正缺点也能实现进步，因此B错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>C：题目主旨是强调在团队活动中需要集体协作，只有集体合作才能获得更大的力量，而不是强调在集体中发展个性，C不符合题意，故C错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>D：材料并没有提到关于角色定位和个人能力提升的相关内容，因此该选项与题意不相符合。因此D错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>因此选A</b></span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）赛龙舟是我国端午节的习俗之一。在龙舟竞技中，每个队员需根据指挥员的鼓点密切配合，保持一致的划桨力度和频率，齐喊口号挥桨劈浪，奋勇争先冲向终点。从中我们可以感受到（ &nbsp; &nbsp;）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）赛龙舟是我国端午节的习俗之一。在龙舟竞技中，每个队员需根据指挥员的鼓点密切配合，保持一致的划桨力度和频率，齐喊口号挥桨劈浪，奋勇争先冲向终点。从中我们可以感受到（    ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/abf52d6d-fb42-45c3-af7f-eab31d0ec96c@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754977962007", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>集体为实现目标团结协作的合作精神</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>只有在集体协作中才能实现自身进步</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>在集体中发展个性需与他人积极合作</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>集体中的角色定位促进个人能力提升</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）赛龙舟是我国端午节的习俗之一。在龙舟竞技中，每个队员需根据指挥员的鼓点密切配合，保持一致的划桨力度和频率，齐喊口号挥桨劈浪，奋勇争先冲向终点。从中我们可以感受到（ &nbsp; &nbsp;）</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39